{"tid":2048720,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[鯊魚]黃金泳灘女子遇溺　送院不治","createTime":"2020-06-03T04:03:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T04:25:27.000Z","uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0dabf6bcd903cb350976582ccc2bc67976de26da","tid":2048720,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T04:03:28.000Z","msg":"今早(3日)6時43分，一名女子在屯門黃金泳灘對開海面游早泳時遇溺，被其他泳客發現及救起。救援人員接報趕至現場時，事主已經陷入昏迷，送院搶救後證實不治。由於事主沒身份證明文件，警員需在泳灘尋找事主的個人物品，以追查其身份及聯絡家人。<br />\n康文署轄下的黃金泳灘，昨晨(2日)有當值救生員發現防鯊網內水域有一條疑似鯊魚的一米長大魚出現，恐傷及泳客，迅速作出廣播，通知及協助泳客返回岸上，又掛紅旗封鎖泳區，禁止泳客落水，有關部門派員到場搜索，但大魚已失去蹤影，防鯊網經檢查未有發現損毀，泳灘於今晨將繼續封閉，直至確定安全後才重開。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200603/bkn-20200603080049518-0603_00822_001.html?refer=hn2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200603%2Fbkn-20200603080049518-0603_00822_001.html%3Frefer%3Dhn2&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgY6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=fc0cd2e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200603/bkn-20200603080049518-0603_00822_001.html?refer=hn2</a>"},{"pid":"66610ed26e95c6e4e4e38a08dd5640f943da0998","tid":2048720,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T04:04:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c20b5fd54ee8ca5673d4219664a33b7e1e5997d3","tid":2048720,"uid":171586,"like":0,"dislike":24,"score":-24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T05:01:37.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"270ceb688df9ce8e3a7c199191a6f47ce53d306f","tid":2048720,"uid":57543,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"c20b5fd54ee8ca5673d4219664a33b7e1e5997d3","tid":2048720,"uid"